node.text: ⚠️GRAPHIC WARNING/SAD BREAKING NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND LET’S PRAY FOR AN GET HELP HERE!⚠️ There’s chaos at Hamid Karzai International Airport in Kabul as Afghans try to flee the T***ban who just took control of Afghanistan, pouring into the capital, Kabul, and meeting little resistance. President Ashraf Ghani fled the country as the Taliban took over the presidential palace and the government collapsed and now gunfire and fear has now gripped the city, with tens of thousands of people trying to escape and witnesses say at least 5 people have died so far following desperate scenes at Kabul airport. Tragic video shows heavy gunfire, people storming the gates and scaling the 10- to 20-foot concrete walls to get onto the airfield with some even trying to cling onto the planes as they took off, with several people falling midair. With all scheduled flights now suspended, many foreigners and Afghans are now stranded as the militants' return to rule brings an end to almost 20 years of a US-led coalition's presence in the country. Please join us in praying for all the people and families now stuck in Afghanistan and share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too as we must make EVERYONE aware of what’s happening here to get them help RIGHT NOW! The International community must not look away so please use your social platform for good and share this now to get help for these people! Via @karmagawa. #prayforkabul #prayforafghanistan #helpkabul #afghantaliban

node.text:
⛰ 💤 Tag your friend who has waaay too much energy in the morning.

Credits: @pang_bang.

Lifting each other up now and always! ❤️ Cinthia Zanuni writes, “Choose for your life someone who has the power to make you feel like you're floating. Choose someone who will make you climb steps in life even if you can't walk on your own legs. Choose someone who decides every day to thank you even if they have reasons to complain.”
Tag a friend who is there for you!

Credits: @cinthiazanuni & @hugoecinthia.
